            , who all gave him a good character.)</p>
               <p>To Larcher. What time did you see the prisoner in the Old Bailey, and the corner of Newgate-street? - I believe it was about seven o'clock when I first<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="178006280223"></xptr> saw him; I parted with him about a quarter after.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17800628-93-verdict475" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17800628-93-verdict475" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
